{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Finished between a.d.","verse":9},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"395 and a.d.","verse":10},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Zechariah, Malachi, Hosea, Joel, Amos.","verse":11},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Finished by a.d.","verse":12},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"The Four Greater Prophets:","verse":13},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Isaiah. a.d.","verse":14},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Ezekiel. a.d.","verse":15},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"Commenced after the death of Eustochium in a.d.","verse":16},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"The commentary on this book, which stops short at chapter xxxii., was therefore written in a.d.","verse":17},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"419, the year which intervened between Eustochium’s death and Jerome’s own.","verse":18},{"book":"Prefaces to the Commentaries.","chapter":1,"text":"We have thought it best to give the Prefaces, as in those to the Vulgate, in the order of the books as they stand in our Bible, not in the order in which they were written.","verse":19}]}